1 Download Arch Linux Iso Here https://archlinux.org/download/
2 Flash The USB Stick
3 On Archiso Run archinstall
4 If You Are On archinstall
-For Disk Configuration ext4
-For Bootloader Limine
-For Kernels linux-lts
-For linux-zen (designed to make a desktop PC feel faster and more responsive)
-Set Hostname
-Set Username And Password
-Set Root Password
-Profile Type Desktop Desktop Environment KDE Plasma
-Network Configuration Network Manager
5 After You Install It
-Enter Konsole
-sudo nano /etc/os-release
-Change NAME="Arch Linux" To NAME="Tritium Linux"
-Change PRETTY_NAME="Arch Linux" To PRETTY_NAME="Tritium Linux"
-Change ID=arch To ID=tritium
-Change HOME_URL"https://archlinux.org/" To HOME_URL="https://github.com/Haikal02-alt/Tritium-Linux"
-Install Firefox sudo pacman -S firefox
-Go To https://github.com/Haikal02-alt/Tritium-Linux Then Follow The tritium-logo.png and tritium-logo-text.png Then Save 2 Photos On Readme To Downloads
-Then sudo mv /home/yourname/Downloads/tritium-logo.png /usr/share/pixmaps
-Then sudo mv /home/yourname/Downloads/tritium-logo-text.png /usr/share/pixmaps
-Then sudo cp /usr/share/pixmaps/tritium-logo.png /usr/share/pixmaps/archlinux-logo.png
-Then sudo cp /usr/share/pixmaps/tritium-logo.png /usr/share/pixmaps/archlinux-logo.svg
-Then sudo cp /usr/share/pixmaps/tritium-logo-text.png /usr/share/pixmaps/archlinux-logo-text.svg
-Then sudo cp /usr/share/pixmaps/tritium-logo-text.png /usr/share/pixmaps/archlinux-logo-text-dark.svg
-Then sudo nano /etc/os-release Then Change LOGO=archlinux-logo to LOGO=/usr/share/pixmaps/tritium-logo.png
-Open Konsole Then Notifications then System Notifications Then Play login and logout sound by click Play a sound Then Click apply
-Click Configure Application Launcher
-Then Change Icon Default KDE To tritium-logo Then Click Apply Then Click OK

Have Fun And Start Using This OS
